@page "/audit"
<h2>Audit</h2>
<p class="text-muted">AuditEvent records are written through the custom API to the FHIR server. Operational audit correlations remain in the application database and must not duplicate clinical payloads.</p>
<ul><li>Login and failed-login events</li><li>Patient viewed or updated</li><li>Diagnostic report viewed</li><li>Data exported</li><li>Break-glass access</li><li>Administrative configuration changes</li></ul>
